#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://github.com/a2aproject/a2a-java/releases/tag/v1.0.0.CR1[1.0.0.CR1] was our feature-complete candidate release. Since then, we focused on cross-SDK interoperability validation and bug fixes."
